              {
                "nodeType": "text",
                "value": "This character swallows every tall tale\u2014buying \u201cdragon tears\u201d from a shady peddler or bowing to a goat they think\u2019s a cursed prince. They\u2019re the village mark, easily duped by charlatans and pranksters alike. Skepticism is a stranger to them, and it shows. Their trusting nature clouds their judgment.",
